Bill McCausland and I looked for Zone-tailed Hawk toward Eagle's Nest Overlook without luck. We saw a Bobcat run across road near there.
SPECIES COMMENTS: Adult seen in flight from summit of Hot Springs Mtn. Unexpected at this time of year.
